{"title":"一道红光照满天（花鼓）","authors":["陈涛"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一道红光照满天（花鼓）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霹雳一声天下惊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中苏会谈在北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个巨人紧握手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫呀和平反战争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一道红光照满天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会谈公报到处传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说会谈意义大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公报呀一字重如山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中苏两国肩并肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在和平最前线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界人民团结紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁拳呀力量大如天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中苏两国爱和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界人民都欢迎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若问那个不高兴？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战争呀贩子一小群！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公报警告侵略者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回头是岸快收兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快滚出约旦去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快呀滚出黎巴嫩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会谈公报胜导弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义心胆战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若想把你狗命保，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快呀收起坏算盘！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}